Puropose of test:
  In a standalone mode, verify the addProduct and getStatus
  operations on the interface IF-DREAM-O-AddProduct.

Prepare:
  Ensure the Ingestion Engine is running.
  The download manager need not be running.

Procedure:
  Execute the python script 'test_addProd.py'

Evaluation:
  The test program reports results on stdout.
  Inspect the log of the Ingestion Engine.
  The addProduct operation should be shown as having run successfully
  for the 'test valid input'.
  There are also some error conditions tested, the log should show
  an approprite error for each of the error condition tests.

